text: A post shared on Instagram claims the late former Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe sent back 1.6 million COVID-19 vaccine doses during the COVID-19 pandemic and also gave citizens ivermectin.
A post shared on Instagram claims Japan halted its COVID-19 vaccine rollout and switched to using ivermectin to combat the spread of the virus.
